item.title: Techfugees Sydney Hackathon 2018
item.description: This hackathon is about developing tech solutions to the challanges refugees face. Hackathon Details, twtr, #Hack4Refugees kickoff Annie introduced the hackathon as a means to bringing ppl together to solve problems. Tech ppl should and can contribute to issues - this is the fourth techfugee hackathon in Sydney. NGO partners: SSI is the largest settlement ngo in Australia Startts works on torture and trauma pick a theme from out of 10, and think about how your product fits needs, who does it help, etc etc.
